The @Eagles owner Jeffrey Lurie: &ldquo;I did look into buying other sports teams when I owned the Eagles, and I regret maybe one of them. There was probably an opportunity to be a significant owner of Arsenal.&ldquo;<br />
<br />
Lurie: &ldquo;I wasn't able to convince enough of the people that were possibly interested in selling at the time. But I saw it similar to the Eagles where it's kind of a difficult stadium situation...I saw it as a refresh (to) energize that franchise, that team.&quot;
